== Sessions ==
Sessions are to be created using the url ( e.g. harryeakins.com:8888/session/elephant )
Sessions are public and require no password
Sessions are identified with a string

Commands:
- Join session - doesn't copy anything
- Sessions are permanent - must manually wipe page

== Infinitely large canvas ==
- Zoom in and out
- Pan
-- Vector information kept only to recreate the image
-- Image rerendered only on resize or panning to previously unseen area of screen
-- Zoomed image shown until rerendering complete

== Touch Screen Compatible ==
- Multitouch

== Simplify ==
- No undoing allowed - just use pen to undo
